X SECTION AND LABEL¶

X SECTION AND LABEL POINT TO implicit-target AND X SECTION AND LABEL POINT TO section-and-label.

X EXPLICIT-TARGET¶

X EXPLICIT-TARGET POINT TO explicit-target AND X EXPLICIT-TARGET POINT TO DUPLICATED ID LIKE id1.

X IMPLICIT SECTION NAME¶

X IMPLICIT SECTION NAME POINT TO implicit-section-name.

X DUPLICATED SUB SECTION¶

`X DUPLICATED SUB SECTION`_ IS BROKEN LINK.

X DUPLICATED SUB SECTION¶

X LABEL BRIDGED TARGET SECTION¶

X bridge label IS NOT TRANSLATABLE BUT LINKED TO TRANSLATED SECTION TITLE.

X bridge label POINT TO LABEL BRIDGED TARGET SECTION AND bridge label2 POINT TO SECTION AND LABEL. THE SECOND APPEARED bridge label2 POINT TO CORRECT TARGET.
